                 <p align="center">
                  <span color="#89141d" face="arial black,avant garde" size="3" style="color: #89141d; font-family: arial black,avant garde; font-size: medium;">

                 <p align="left">
                  <span face="arial black,avant garde" size="3" style="font-family: arial black,avant garde; font-size: medium;">
                   Grab an ice cold brew featuring an assortment of local and domestic beer.  Enjoy a glass or a bottle of red, white or blush wine with dinner.  Choose between a variety of our homemade Sangria that is loaded with fresh fruit.  Our non-alcoholic selection includes fountain drinks, ice tea, various juice, hot tea, and coffee.  Ice water is also availible upon request.
                  </span>
                  <span face="arial black,avant garde" size="3" style="font-family: arial black,avant garde; font-size: medium;">
                   <br/>
                   <br/>
                   Tantalize your palate with our mouth-watering clams &amp; oysters on the half shell. Pick out the exact size clam that you enjoy while our bartenders shuck your order to perfection in front of the consumer. We carry the finest local oysters availible and we serve these shellfish delights with homemade cocktail sauce, horseraddish, hot sauce, and/or lemon wedges.
